Haxe syntax highlighting 

#------------------------
automatic install:
#------------------------
for root:
1) run: sudo install.sh
2) restart gedit

for user:
1) run: install.sh
2) restart gedit


#------------------------
manual install:
#------------------------
for root: 
1) copy: haxe.lang to: /usr/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs
2) copy: haxe.xml to: /usr/share/mime/packages
3) run: sudo update-mime-database /usr/share/mime
4) restart gedit

for user:
1) copy: haxe.lang to: ~/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs
2) copy: haxe.xml to: ~/.local/share/mime/packages
3) run: update-mime-database ~/.local/share/mime
4) restart gedit

(Create folders where necessary.)
